trans-unit.source: An in-memory collection of hash tables that allows the rapid lookup of designer elements by <xref:System.Type>.
trans-unit.target: En InMemory-samling hash-tabeller som tillåter snabb sökning designer element av <xref:System.Type>.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The metadata store contains custom attribute metadata, such as the association between designers and types.
trans-unit.target: Metadata-arkivet innehåller Attributmetadata, till exempel associationen mellan designers och typer.

trans-unit.source: Custom attributes can be defined in an <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable> and added to the metadata store.
trans-unit.target: Anpassade attribut kan definieras i en <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>och läggs till i arkivet för metadata.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>

trans-unit.source: After the attributes are added, they will appear in calls made to <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>.
trans-unit.target: När attribut har lagts till, visas de i anrop till <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>

trans-unit.source: Adds the given table to the current <xref href="System.AppDomain"></xref> object’s attribute store.
trans-unit.target: Lägger till den angivna tabellen i aktuellt <xref href="System.AppDomain"> </xref> objektets attributarkiv.

trans-unit.source: After the table is added, calls to <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor> will use attributes defined in the newly added table.
trans-unit.target: När tabellen läggs anrop till <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>kommer att använda attribut som definierats i tabellen nytillagda.</xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>

trans-unit.source: Multiple tables can be added to the attribute store.
trans-unit.target: Flera tabeller kan läggas till attributarkivet.

trans-unit.source: In the case of conflicts, attributes in the most recently added table are used.
trans-unit.target: Vid konflikter används attribut i den nyligen tillagda tabellen.
Tabellen som används för att lägga till.
